songs.title: Pancakes & Syrup
songs.album: Yo Gabba Gabba! Music Is... Awesome! Vol. 4
songs.lyrics:
It's breakfast time!
Pancakes and syrup, pancakes and syrup, pancakes and syrup, it's breakfast time! (x2)
Y'all know me, I biz with the beat guaranteed to rock out just like the E. Leave the M-A-R-K-I-E ain't know why there's a ZAY-Y-P. Every time I rock from here to Europe, you know I be makin' pancakes an syrup. Yup, uh-huh, I rub my tummy, yum-yum-yum -yum-yum-yum-yummy!
Refrain
Eat 'em up, eat 'em up, eat 'em up, yum yum yum yum yum yum yum, eat 'em up . Eat 'em up, eat 'em up eat 'em up, yum, yum eat 'em up eat 'em up
Yum, pancakes, pancakes syrup! Yum yum eat 'em up eat 'em up eat 'em up. Yum pancakes, pancakes syrup, eeeeeeeat 'em up
Refrain
Hey, what's that y'all doin'?! That's it right there, I ain't wanna hear nothin'!
